CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, page 9, reads: "Homemakers See Latest in Foods, Appliances...3. Edward Carter, one of Supreme Liberty Life Insurance Company's representatives, signs up Mr. and Mrs. Leonard Wright, the Home Service Fair bride and groom...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Edward Carter seated with Mr. and Mrs. Leonard Wright in Supreme Liberty Life Insurance Company booth for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair in the Hunt Armory
